  <summary date="2025-03-31T18:41:11Z" status="Introduced in Senate">EAGLES Act of 2025

This bill reauthorizes the National Threat Assessment Center (NTAC) within the U.S. Secret Service.

It reauthorizes the functions of NTAC through FY2030 and expands them to include additional activities related to the prevention of targeted violence, such as the establishment of a national program on targeted school violence prevention.</summary>
